{"id":"e6859040-a5d5-4c25-bf4e-9a4030bb8b4b","name":"Camp Half-blood","description":"<h1><img src=\"https://ella.janitorai.com/media-approved/D1YhB6s4l9ktpOi8MLU8y.webp\"></h1><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>You make the story! </em></strong></span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>This bot can do: </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/Omegaverse\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><strong><em>Omegaverse</em></strong></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, rockstar au, dark au, villain/hero au. </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://en.wikipedia.org/wiki/N%C4%81ga\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>Nagas</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, werewolfs, vampires, office romance, back in time stories, historical, fantasy, apocalypse, </em></span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://shield-hero.fandom.com/wiki/Demi-Human#:~:text=Edit,protruding%20somewhere%20on%20the%20body.\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>demi-humans</em></span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(0, 196, 227);\"><em>, and many more! try it out yourself!</em></span></p><hr><h1></h1><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\">what does \"you make the story mean?\" it means the bot is open promted, allowing you the freedom of choice, big stories, small stories, scenarios all at your own discression, you dont have to be locked by others ideas, here you can do exactly what you want with the bots without them trying to correct your actions and behaviour.</h5><h5 style=\"text-align: center;\"></h5><p style=\"text-align: center;\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"><strong>Camp Half-Blood</strong> is a Greek </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Demigod\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">demigod</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> training facility located on the north shore of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Long_Island\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Long Island.</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> The camp is directed by the god </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Dionysus\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Dionysus</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, who the campers call \"Mr. D,\" and </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Chiron\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Chiron</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, a </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Centaur\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Centaur</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> who is the activities director. It is also the </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Greece\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Greek</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> counterpart of </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Camp_Jupiter\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Camp Jupiter</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">, a </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/Roman_Empire\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">Roman</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> camp between Oakland, </span><a rel=\"noopener noreferrer\" href=\"https://riordan.fandom.com/wiki/California\" target=\"_blank\"><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\">California</span></a><span style=\"color: rgb(255, 255, 255);\"> and Berkley, California.</span></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\"></p><p style=\"text-align: center;\">Please be patient with these type of bots they have a lot of people to keep track off, if it doesnt fully grasp their personality you can always coax it by writing for the character for a moment OR narrate their usu","personality":"","scenario":"","first_message":"","avatar":"d1db66e6-df4a-4c0d-8675-1c8838b536c2_3f0f2f84-5e71-474b-8acf-ff71ffde3d49.webp","creator":"SomethingClever","creator_verified":true,"nsfw":true,"tags":["👭 Multiple","🎲 RPG","👤 AnyPOV","🌗 Switch"],"chats":15461,"messages":763435,"created_at":"2024-12-05T00:52:44.202019+00:00"}